long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A chrome extension to note youtube views of any video played at different times.
All one has to do is click on the extension after playing the video . Also runs in background , notes a youtube videos view count every 10 seconds. 
And Extension will keep list of all the views noted.
